" the key generation process."
msgstr ""

#: ../../pro/linux/openpgp-key-generation-using-gpa.md:18
#: ../../pro/openpgp-key-generation-using-gpa.md:18
#: ../../pro/windows/openpgp-key-generation-using-gpa.md:18
